{%- comment -%}
  ============================================================================
  HTML-PRODUCT-PAYMENTS
  ============================================================================
  Payment method icons display.

  PARAMETERS:
  - method_1 through method_5: Payment method keys (visa, mastercard, etc.)

  SUPPORTED METHODS:
  visa, mastercard, amex, paypal, ideal, bancontact, klarna, 
  apple_pay, google_pay, shop_pay, maestro, sofort
  ============================================================================
{%- endcomment -%}

